description: This home seamlessly blends modern elegance with everyday comfort, offering a serene retreat while keeping you close to all that South Boston has to offer. This stunning 3-bedroom PLUS office, 3.5-bathroom duplex, spanning 2,427 sq. ft., features meticulously designed living spaces w/ high-end finishes throughout. The main level boasts an open-concept layout, highlighted by 9-inch wide white oak floors, soaring ceilings & custom library wall. A 12-foot quartz island, gas fireplace, Thermador appliances & private deck make this space ideal for entertaining. The dedicated office with paneled French doors & a stylish powder room add to the home’s functionality.  On the lower level, you'll find 3 spacious bedrooms, each w/ custom closet systems, & 3 full bathrooms, incl. two en-suite. The primary suite features a spa-style bath, walk-in closet, & private deck. In-unit laundry, abundant storage & direct-access parking. Moments from Thomas Park, the Beaches, East & West Broadway.
